1.0.0
Initial release
- release includes main configuration for Adobe Commerce 2.4 stack with PHP 7.4, 8.1 and 8.2 on board
- release includes elasticsearch 7 and opensearch as well
- additional information specified in package doc

Changes since 1.0.0b
- removed obsolete compose version field
- removed public IPAM subnet and let Docker choose a private range
- fixed MariaDB env var to use MARIADB_PASSWORD
- fixed OpenSearch plugin list command typo
- added PHP 8.3, 8.4 and 8.5 support
- configured nginx to use SSL
- added SSL certificate generation script
- added init script which includes mkcert installation required for certificate generation